title: Ep. 1057 - Daya Teases Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya and Jetha are spending quality time together when a waiter interrupts them. He gets them a bouquet of flowers. Daya keeps teasing. Meanwhile, the waiter comes back again.

title: Ep. 1058 - Tapu Sena's Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As 26th January is approaching, Tapu sena comes up with a plan to celebrate 26th Jan in a grand way. They inform Bhide and Madhavi that they would be the chief guests for the day.

title: Ep. 1059 - The Chief Guests - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu sena come and inform Jetha and Daya that thy would become the chief guests for the event on 26th Jan. Daya is elated listening to the news.

title: Ep. 1060 - Chachaji's Words Of Wisdom - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: When Champaklal goes for his  morning walk, his friends question him on various things. They also say he has an extremely respecting son.

title: Ep. 1061 - Daya Has A Request - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya calls up Jetha to inform that guests are coming home. She lures him by tasty food to come home early. She decides on making the food ready and delicious.

title: Ep. 1062 - Daya's Demands - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya asks Jetha for the money that he took from her to pay for the other services. She demands extra money from him to look into the household chores.

title: Ep. 1063 - A Mishap - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer is happy about his presentation. Meanwhile, when Babita gives him tea, it slips and falls on the laptop. Iyer panics about the same. They try finding a solution.

title: Ep. 1064 - Where Is Bagha? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita goes to Jetha's shop to get her work done. When she returns, she informs that Bagah has been sent somewhere by Jetha. Daya calls up Jetha to enquire the same. Nattu kaka is also worried.

title: Ep. 1065 - Taunting Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Popatlal find Jetha walking around with a  bag and laptop. They intedn to tease him. Jetha gets irritated with the same.

title: Ep. 1066 - The Kids Play Smart - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Harsh is standing outside playing a game on his phone. Tapu and his friends eye on the same. They trick him by saying that they have a robot and take his phone in return to play with it.

title: Ep. 1067 - Tapu Tricks Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is irritated with Tapu and decides to teach him a lesson. Tapu, on the other tricks him by giving the phone to Champaklal and he scolds him.

title: Ep. 1068 - Where Is The Ring? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha has lost his ring and Daya is trying her best to find out where it has disappeared. Meanwhile, Iyer leaves no stone upturned in pulling Jetha's leg.

title: Ep. 1069 - The Kids Have A Request - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After knowing that Tapu is getting a phone, the other kids decide to request their parents for a phone. The parents try to convince their kids to not have one.

title: Ep. 1070 - Tapu Is Anxious - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu is really anxious is getting his new phone. He goes and wakes up Jetha who is in deep sleep. Meanwhile, Chachaji shouts on Jetha for waking up late.

title: Ep. 1071 - Where Is Sonu's Phone? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The kids are happy as they have got their new phones. Meanwhile, while checking for the phones, Sonu doesn't find hers and Golu has it with him.
